Opens a Long position when the price crosses above SMA10 and subsequently reaches at least 15 points above that average — confirming the strength of the upward move. Closes the position when the price drops at least 12 points below SMA10 — signaling a trend reversal. Both parameters (15 pts entry, 12 pts exit) are configurable in the indicator settings.
